data.description: Discover the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and community in this exquisite 2-story, 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home, nestled in a family-friendly neighborhood that has a pool and park. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and welcoming floor plan. The spacious living room with large windows offers a view of the manicured front yard. The chef's kitchen is a culinary haven with high-end appliances, granite countertops, a center island, and pantry. It seamlessly connects to the dining area, creating the perfect backdrop for both intimate family dinners and lively gatherings. The lower-level master suite is a true sanctuary, complete with a walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom featuring a walk-in shower. It's your private oasis to escape and rejuvenate. Three additional spacious bedrooms on the second floor offer flexibility and comfort for your family or guests. Each bedroom is designed with comfort and functionality in mind. A convenient half bath on the main floor is perfect for guests. Conveniently located near top-rated schools, shopping centers, and parks, this home offers the ideal blend of suburban tranquility and urban convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional house your forever home. Schedule a showing today and experience the luxury, comfort, and sense of community this property has to offer. Your dream home in the perfect neighborhood awaits!
